  "page_help": "Rubatsiro & FAQ",
  "help_system_title": "📋 System Description",
  "help_system_desc1": "FastWrite ibasa rinocherekedzwa ramutongi wako retora zvinyorwa (akaunti, mari, nhau) rusununguko kuchangaradza (AI). Zvinotowanya munzvimbo dzako chete — zvinyorwa zvako hazvinoshearedzwa nemunhu upi zvake, kusanganisira mureza weplatform.",
  "help_system_desc2": "Zvinoita chii: Unofora PDF ine akaunti imwe kana dzimwe. Iyo iyo inogadzira kugeza pamberi akaunti, inowana mugambi, inofanana namumiriro wazvisimbiso, ndetora zvinyorwa zvawatamba (nambari yekiakaundi, zuva, mari, zvinhu zvemhando, nezvimwe). Pakupera kweiyo, unoshanda zvinyorwa kuvaDzambi kana Excel.",
  "help_workflow_title": "🔄 Shanda — Sitepe neSitepe",
  "help_step1_title": "Misa API Key",
  "help_step1_desc": "Enda kuSettings → API Keys nyora yako AI key (semuenzaniso Google Gemini). Ichi chikudikanwa — platform haizvitori nayo key. Kumali kufanirwa mudare reAI yako.",
  "help_step2_title": "Kwakura Mazwi",
  "help_step2_desc": "Enda kuUpload & Extract. Dzakara kana sora faira re PDF (kusvika 200 akaunti pafaira) napusha \"Register Documents\". Iyo iyo inogadzira kutora akaunti nemugambi.",
  "help_step3_title": "Buritsa Zvisimbiso",
  "help_step3_desc": "Kubva kuDocuments peji, sora mazvinyorwa amwe kana apo zvakadaro napusha \"Labels\". Unofanirwa kupinda papeji yadandemutano ipapo unowanikwa akaunti kuruoko rweshoure neparugo rwezvisimbiso kuruoko rweshumba. Rondedzwa zvinhu zvaunoda kutora (semuenzaniso nambari yekiakaundi, zuva, mari, VAT) nozvinhu zvemhando. Mugai, buritsa zvisimbiso kubvaLabels peji → + New Label.",
  "help_step4_title": "Tora Zvinyorwa (Batch)",
  "help_step4_desc": "Kubva kuDocuments peji, sora mazvinyorwa napusha \"Batch\". Iyo iyo inogadza kushandisa AI etora zvinyorwa zvakabatanidzwa neasingano dzepamberi deiyo. Maidzo anokumira mutable yemazvinyorwa.",
  "help_step5_title": "Ongorora & Vira",
  "help_step5_desc": "Kubva kuDocuments peji, sora mazvinyorwa napusha \"Approve\". Unowana akaunti kuruoko rweshoure nozvinhu zvakatorwa kuruoko rweshumba. Buritsa zvavaki napusha \"Approve Invoice\". Kusanganisa kwesalera kunofanana nzvimbo yenzwi munhairo zvichiwinirwa.",
  "help_step6_title": "Simukanisa Mafaira",
  "help_step6_desc": "Mazvinyorwa akavira, budzai kuDocuments peji. Sora mazvinyorwa akavira napusha \"CSV\", \"XLSX\" kana \"Line Items XLSX\" kuSimukanisa. Kana kusazonaka, mazvinyorwa ese akavira achakumirira.",
  "help_tip_title": "💡 Mubvunzo",
  "help_tip_text": "Munzira yakati, ndiyo: Upload → Labels → Batch → Approve → Export. Kutanga buritsa zvisimbiso zvezvinhu zvese zveiyo akaunti (semuenzaniso DEI, COSMOTE, VODAFONE) ipapo kumira kuwakura kwekuwakura. Unogara wakabatanidza zvisimbiso, iyo iyo inofanana zwakawanda kuakaunti matsva kubva kumumigambi.",
